Package: ucc
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends},
         systemd,
         tuxedo-drivers,
         qt6-qpa-plugins
Recommends: ucc-gui, ucc-tray
Description: Uniwill Control Center - System control daemon and tools
 Uniwill Control Center (UCC) is a comprehensive system control application
 suite for TUXEDO computers. This package provides the core daemon and utilities.
 .
 Features:
  - Fan control management
  - Keyboard backlight control
  - Display settings
  - CPU power management
  - Water cooler monitoring and control
  - System monitoring

Package: ucc-gui
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends},
         ucc (= ${binary:Version}),
         qt6-base (>= 6.0),
         libkf6windowsystem6
Description: Uniwill Control Center - Graphical user interface
 Main graphical user interface for Uniwill Control Center.
 Provides full control over system settings and monitoring.

Package: ucc-tray
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends},
         ucc (= ${binary:Version}),
         qt6-base (>= 6.0)
Description: Uniwill Control Center - System tray applet
 System tray application for quick access to Uniwill Control Center
 features and status monitoring.
